description.narrative: Under the leadership of Department of Health and National Nutrition Council, UNICEF and partners supported the development of key nutrition policies, and the Implementing Rules and Regulations of RA 11148 - the Kalusugan at Nutrisyon ng Mag-Nanay Act (the First 1000 Days Act). The Rules and Regulations provide national policy guidance for strengthening nutrition governance, scaling up both preventive and therapeutic nutrition-specific and nutrition-sensitive interventions. At the Provincial and Municipal level, UNICEF also provided strategic technical support in developing multi-sectoral nutrition and WASH plans and strengthening subnational capacities to plan, deliver and monitor quality services even during emergencies. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:07/02/2020
